ssment.during the synchronous sessions, you will be invited to contribute ideas, make decisions, and ask questions about the course (re)design process.optimizing your course experience we have designed this course for a single learner per registration.if you need to miss one or more of the live webcasts that accompany the course but wish to participate in the asynchronous activities and receive feedback on your assignments, you will be able to watch recordings of each session via the course site within a few days of each session’s broadcast.